need a circus in town.

04:43.091 --> 04:45.510
You boys be careful
with

04:45.593 --> 04:46.594
your brother.

04:46.678 --> 04:48.680
Ah, Ma, Will can hold
his own.

04:48.763 --> 04:49.806
You saw him.

04:49.889 --> 04:51.349
You hold your
tongue, boy.

04:51.433 --> 04:55.395
Yes, ma'am.
C'mon, guys, leave

04:55.478 --> 04:56.604
him alone.

04:56.688 --> 05:01.026
Will, no.
You cannot do that.

05:01.109 --> 05:03.028
Do you understand?

05:03.111 --> 05:05.196
You boys should grow
up.

05:05.280 --> 05:07.032
What do you know
about growin' up?

