to work.

08:03.333 --> 08:06.461
You're
up to bat.

08:07.962 --> 08:08.963
Come
on, let's go!

08:10.465 --> 08:12.300
What?
What is it?

08:12.801 --> 08:15.136
Stop.
Everyone, come in here.

08:21.476 --> 08:23.728
I'd like
to play baseball.

08:23.812 --> 08:26.398
You
want to play baseball?

08:27.023 --> 08:29.192
Yes.

08:30.694 --> 08:36.073
You're
too small.

08:36.157 --> 08:38.243
And too skinny.

08:38.326 --> 08:40.745
I want to
play.

08:40.828 --> 08:43.248
Okay.
Let's see what you got.

08:43.331 --> 08:46.167
You bat
first.

08:55.677 --> 09:00.432
Nope.
Move back.

09:00.515 --> 09:01.349
There.

09:03.184 --> 09:06.771
Put
your hands closer together

09:06.855 --> 09:08.648
and spread your feet apart.

09:08.732 --> 09:10.900
Back a
little more.

09:18.700 --> 09:19.909
You
have to swing at the ball.

09:39.220 --> 09:42.682
Three strikes, you're
out, kid.

09:42.766 --> 09:45.644
Let's see if you can
catch a ball.

09:45.727 --> 09:47.228
Take the field.

09:57.572 --> 09:59.824
Yes,
right there.

09:59.908 --> 10:02.077
He is going to hit the ball to
you.

10:17.258 --> 10:22.138
You'll
never make it.

10:34.776 --> 10:39.114
Good job.
Be careful.

11:28.330 --> 11:31.750
It's time to
come in.

11:31.833 --> 11:33.168
Give it to me.

11:53.521 --> 11:56.691
I've
been watching you.

11:59.361 --> 12:01.613
You've
been watching me?

12:01.696 --> 12:06.284
Yes.
For months.

12:06.368 --> 12:07.827
Why?

12:07.911 --> 12:10.121
You
want to play baseball, right?

12:10.205 --> 12:11.164
That's
right.

12:11.247 --> 12:12.957
You
can't.

12:13.041 --> 12:14.292
You're
too small.

12:14.376 --> 12:17.128
You
already told me that.

12:17.712 --> 12:20.799
You're
going to

12:20.882 --> 12:24.135
get a lot of that.
People will tease you.

12:24.219 --> 12:29.849
You need to be better
than everyone.

12:29.933 --> 12:35.480
It doesn't matter if you are
small or deaf.

12:35.563 --> 12:38.358
The great thing about
us being deaf

12:38.441 --> 12:41.319
is that we don't have to hear
what they say.

12:41.403 --> 12:44.656
You can stay
completely focused.

12:44.739 --> 12:47.409
Let me show you how I
practice throwing strikes.

13:03.591 --> 13:07.721
When
you can hit that

13:07.804 --> 13:12.934
square consistently, that's when
you know you're good.

13:13.768 --> 13:14.769
Watch.

13:24.612 --> 13:26.698
Better
than

13:26.781 --> 13:27.949
anyone.
Understand?

13:58.146 --> 13:59.397
I think
you're ready.

