The team is going to
be barnstorming across Ohio

14:04.986 --> 14:06.237
and the Midwest.

14:06.321 --> 14:08.740
We need one more
player.

14:08.823 --> 14:10.158
What do you say? h

14:11.326 --> 14:18.166
We're called the Ohio
Independents.

14:32.722 --> 14:34.516
Come on, run!
Let's go!

14:34.599 --> 14:35.433
Let's go!
Run!

15:11.886 --> 15:18.184
Safe!

15:18.268 --> 15:25.483
Good game.

15:25.567 --> 15:29.863
I
taught you well.

15:29.946 --> 15:33.158
We just beat a very good team.

15:33.241 --> 15:37.704
You deaf boys
play pretty good.

15:37.787 --> 15:42.917
White boys usually don't
normally shake our hands.

15:53.762 --> 15:56.848
Hearing boys usually
don't tell us we

