here.

56:47.048 --> 56:49.718
Son of a gun.

57:22.917 --> 57:24.210
Great game.

57:24.294 --> 57:27.505
Oh, yeah, it is.

57:27.589 --> 57:28.840
Hello.

57:28.923 --> 57:31.051
Hi. Are you deaf?

57:31.134 --> 57:33.845
You got
me.

57:33.928 --> 57:37.182
You play baseball
very well.

57:37.265 --> 57:39.893
Thank
you.

57:39.976 --> 57:41.728
Are you from Urbana?

57:41.811 --> 57:44.022
No, Cincinnati.

57:44.105 --> 57:48.568
You came
all this way to watch me play?

57:48.652 --> 57:51.363
I don't even know
you, sir.

57:51.446 --> 57:55.867
