This is some joke, right?

01:07:25.353 --> 01:07:29.441
Dooley's playin' me for some
damn fool.

01:07:29.524 --> 01:07:33.945
You don't understand?

01:07:34.029 --> 01:07:40.452
I said this is a joke.
A joke.

01:07:40.535 --> 01:07:45.290
